	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have just started my second character, a DE Wizard, and have a few questions.<br><br>Where to lvl?<br>1-5 Netekulos<br>6-8 N. Ro<br>9-11 Commons (whisps)<br>12-17 Lava Storm<br>18-25 Over There<br>26-? Not sure...<br><br>Kiting vs Root and Nuke<br>Is B of F that much better than than Root? I would think root would be better as it allows you time med if need be. Thats just my newbie take on it. Shadow step and root again if the root breaks, and repeat.<br><br>Area of Effect Spells.<br>I hear alot about these. Some people swear by tem, others hate them. How do you use them effectivley?<br><br>Weapon<br>I wasted half a day trying to get the fear dagger in lesser fay. Couldn't find an undead sprite. Do they still spawn? Any suggestions on a replacement?<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
