	   <tr><td colspan=2>hi there,<br><br>I've seen a lot of post on tips for low lvl's, but here's some nice places to hunt when you are at a higher lvl's:<br>lvl 16-30: Only one place, Lake of Ill Omen. Excellent experience and I had no hassle finding groups, and the money loot isn't bad.<br><br>lvl 30-38: OverThere (OT). You can kill in grp's with also excellent exp. Most mobs drops a couple of pp per kill.<br><br>lvl 38-up: Dreadlands.<br><br>Enjoy your hunting!<br><br>Minior<br>Ayonae Ro<br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
