	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello. At the time of ost, my wizzie is of the 19th circle. Several people have posted great information, so there is probably no need for me to take up more space. BUT I'M BORED lol!!! Anyway, here is my level starategy. I started in Freeport. For those of you that didnt you should go there and get a bind, because Freeport is the place to be. Anyway, here it is:<br><br>Levels 1-2: Kill snakes and rats until lvl 3. That's easy.<br>Level 3-4: Go into Northern Ro and kill fire beetles. I know there are fire beetles in freeport, but nro is less crowded, and therefore more beetles are yours. Once you ding to lvl 5:<br>Level 5-6: kill bats and lots of bats and sell the wings for 2pp a stack (a stack is 20). When you have 17pp, buy a backpack and fill it with bone chips (pay no more than 2pp a stack). Hitch a ride on the boat in east freeport and sail to the butcherblock mountains. Follow the path to Kaladim. Go to the paladin's guild (you may need to get a guide, or find a map online) and find Gunlock Jure. He gives a bone chips quest, use up ALL of your bone chips on this. You should reach lvl 7 with an entire backpack.<br>Levels 7-9: Go back to freeport, and then into the eastern commonlands. Get into an orc group till ya ding to 10.<br>Levels 10-13: Kill dervish cutthroats in nro. Nice loot for that lvl. At 14:<br>Level 14: Kill orcs in oasis.<br>Level 15 on: Kill either dw crcs in a group or ogres in tims deep (also ina group). I'm gonna do this till like lvl 22, then go somewhere else.<br><br>Good luck wizzies!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
