	   <tr><td colspan=2>One last post all. STRATEGY LOL. Well I will give a list of where i hunted from 1 on.<br>LVL 1-12<br>Stay around gfay bb area. Kill orcs, scarabs, skellys at chess board whatever till your 12 hard time but you will get their in no time.<br>LVL 12-19 FAST!!!<br>Ok now throw most your money in the bank and all extra weight you wont need. Get a tp to north karana and head into south karana. Get to the Lake Rathe ent and zone in. Go past the gnolls and follow the wall to the right.&lt;good place to work up the ol swimming!&gt; You will run into the arena. Here you will kill little aviaks until they are blue and green. LVL 15 or so. Then if you cant get in a group head over to the hermit.<br>ROOT dont let him get ahold of you!!!. NUKE NUKE NUKE NUKE NUKE..hmm..he's dead WOW full bub of blue exp. easy enough. you can kill him till around your 18th lvl or so then go kill aviak guards. <br>LVL 20-26<br>hmm...ok two choices here hunt in south karana at kfc or take on the gnolls at the spires in a gnoll group. Or you can go to lake of ill omen. I hate lake of ill omen got really bored their so you make your choice. <br>LVL 26-30+<br>GNOLLS GNOLLS GNOLLS...south karana for me good exp good loot good fun need i say more?!<br><br>Side note: DONT BE TO SCARED OF VELIOUSE!!! You can take the boat over and kill cougars with a group at the pirate camp at about 29. I saw tons of low lvls their doing great. If you get one on you solo...stop where you know you are and just take it like a grain of salt..CR..the life of a wizzy huh? LOL =)<br><br>Be safe out their. You can become powerfull but only the really good ones make it to high lvls and reap the rewards of their hard times!!!<br>Peent<br>LVL 32 wizard Torvonilous<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
